OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FA Royal Marines recruit escaped from
OL,7,Fthe naval base where he was training
OL,8,Fwhile a security camera was pointing
OL,9,Fat the ground, an inquest into his
OL,10,Fdeath has heard.
OL,12,FConnor Clark, 18, from Norfolk, was
OL,13,Fjust three weeks into his military
OL,14,Fcareer when his body was discovered on
OL,15,Fthe tracks adjacent to the Commando
OL,16,FTraining Centre in Lympstone, Devon,
OL,17,Fon the morning of 12 June 2021.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
