OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FHe told the hearing it was a blur and
OL,7,Fdifficult to make out in the darkness.
OL,8,FHe said it only became obvious after
OL,9,Fsunrise when the light improved.
OL,11,FMajor Mark Latham said there were
OL,12,Finsufficient staff at the time to
OL,13,Fcarry out all the duties.
OL,15,FHe believed the security staff may
OL,16,Fhave focused their efforts on
OL,17,Fsupervising the main entry points
OL,18,Fduring the middle of the night.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
