OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FHe said that the camera either
OL,7,Fsuffered a malfunction at 2.20pm or
OL,8,Fhad been left in that position.
OL,10,FHe said that particular camera was
OL,11,Ftemperamental, but was working
OL,12,Fperfectly at 3.50pm.
OL,14,FMr Hughes was asked, "If you assume
OL,15,Fthe camera was working between 0220
OL,16,Fand 0350 would it have picked up
OL,17,FConnor Clark leaving the base?"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
