PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FHe replied that yes, there was "a
OL,7,Fstrong possibility" it would have
OL,8,Fdone, but he added it also "depended
OL,9,Fon the camera pointing in the right
OL,10,Fdirection".
OL,12,FMr Hughes added that he couldn't
OL,13,Frecall whether either him or his
OL,14,Fcolleagues had carried out foot
OL,15,Fpatrols during the night.
OL,17,FSecurity staff may have been attending
OL,18,Fan 'incident at the main gate'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
