OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FWhen asked by the coroner Phillip
OL,7,FSpinney why someone may have been
OL,8,Ftaken off the role of operating the
OL,9,FCCTV cameras, he said there was an
OL,10,Fincident at the main gate.
OL,12,FHe said he remembered three drunk
OL,13,Fpeople attempting to bring a female
OL,14,Finto the camp who was unauthorised and
OL,15,Farguments broke out at the gate.
OL,17,FIt went back and forth until they
OL,18,Feventually drove off in a drunken
OL,19,Fstate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
