OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FBackground: Recruit given 'so many
OL,7,Fchances' by superiors after making
OL,8,Fmistakes
OL,10,FThe inquest also heard that Connor
OL,11,FClark had failed a couple of kit
OL,12,Finspections but had been re-inspected
OL,13,Fby an officer and passed, but was then
OL,14,Fpulled up by an instructor for a
OL,15,Fmistake during drill training.
OL,17,FHe had also made comments about being
OL,18,Fa "failure" and the "worst recruit"
OL,19,Fand had also misplaced a blank firing
OL,20,Fadapter for his rifle.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
