OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FMarine Charles Dryden, who had
OL,7,Fundertaken the ROP course with Mr
OL,8,FClark, told the inquest his friend had
OL,9,Fbeen criticised by a corporal.
OL,11,F"We were learning the basics of
OL,12,Fmarching," Marine Dryden said.
OL,14,F"During this, Connor made a mistake
OL,15,Fand the instructor said if he had his
OL,16,Fway, he wouldn't have given him so
OL,17,Fmany chances with the previous
OL,18,Finspections and would have put him
OL,19,Fback to the start of the training. It
OL,20,Fwasn't his decision, however.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
