OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,F"This was not a singling out of Connor
OL,7,Fand the instructor had said similar
OL,8,Fthings to other recruits who had made
OL,9,Fmistakes."
OL,11,FThe witness, who is now a member of 47
OL,12,FCommando, said some of the instructors
OL,13,Fcould shout and swear at recruits if
OL,14,Fthey made mistakes but there was also
OL,15,Fbanter.
OL,17,FThe inquest has previously heard that,
OL,18,Ftwo days before Mr Clark died, he had
OL,19,Fgone to the sick bay seeking treatment
OL,20,Ffor an injury to his elbow.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
