OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FHe told medical staff he had initially
OL,7,Fcut his elbow when he fell against a
OL,8,Fradiator but then had used a knife to
OL,9,Freopen the wound to avoid duties.
OL,11,FAfter the wound was dressed, he had
OL,12,Freturned to training, where one of the
OL,13,Finstructors questioned why he had been
OL,14,Fin the sick bay - causing the lesson
OL,15,Fto be taught again.
OL,17,F"Connor replied that he was going to
OL,18,Fput his chit in anyway," Marine Dryden
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
