OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,F"The instructor replied along the
OL,7,Flines of 'While you're here and
OL,8,Fgetting paid you are going to learn
OL,9,Fwhat I am going to teach you'."
OL,11,FThe inquest heard that the other
OL,12,Frecruits were helping Mr Clark find
OL,13,Fthe blank firing adapter for his rifle
OL,14,Fbecause they did not want to receive a
OL,15,Ftroop physical punishment - known as a
OL,16,F"thrashing".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
