OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,F"I wouldn't disagree that you couldn't
OL,7,Fgo to an instructor and get a new one,
OL,8,Fbut I would definitely agree that at
OL,9,Fthat point there would have been
OL,10,Frepercussions for losing that piece of
OL,11,Fequipment," Marine Dryden said.
OL,13,F"From what I recall, other recruits
OL,14,Fsaid they would help him find it and
OL,15,Fnot say anything due to the thought of
OL,16,Fthe whole troop getting thrashed and
OL,17,Fpotentially losing the weekend leave
OL,18,Fwe were due to get on the Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
