OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,F"I think there was always a fear that
OL,7,Fpotentially it would not be granted,
OL,8,Fif standards were not met."
OL,10,FHe also rejected claims that there was
OL,11,Fa "hostile environment" between
OL,12,Frecruits and did not remember any
OL,13,Fphysical confrontations.
OL,15,F"It was a high-pressure environment
OL,16,Fand there was the stress of the
OL,17,Fcourse, but I don't remember physical
OL,18,Fconfrontations," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
