OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,FThe witness said he was shocked at his
OL,7,Ffriend's death, having only spoken to
OL,8,Fhim the evening before about his plans
OL,9,Fto continue with the training course.
OL,11,F"At that point I didn't think Connor
OL,12,Fwould have taken his own life because
OL,13,Fhe was missing at that point, I
OL,14,Fpersonally thought it was a cry for
OL,15,Fhelp," he said.
OL,17,F"I guess it is hard to believe that a
OL,18,Fperson who I spoke to the night before
OL,19,Fwould do that and seemed OK the night
OL,20,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
