OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1718848656
OL,3,CStruggling recruit escaped base while
OL,4,CCCTV camera 'pointed at the ground'
OL,6,F"Obviously everyone was saddened by
OL,7,FConnor's death but agreed that we
OL,8,Fdidn't necessarily attribute that to
OL,9,Fhim being bullied by the corporals or
OL,10,Fanything like that."
OL,12,FThe inquest continues.
